== 反響 ==
電影贏得了正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度高達93%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/southside_with_you/ |title=Southside with You |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=August 25, 2016 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208041047/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/southside_with_you |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分75<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/southside-with-you|title=Southside with You reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=August 25, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108171458/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/southside-with-you|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要受影評人稱讚其演員的演技、對白和浪漫的氛圍使人愉悅。

分析師評估電影於首映週末在八百零六間戲院終能獲得200萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Could Suffocate ‘Suicide Squad’ During Sluggish Summer Weekend: Box Office Preview |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160825120030/http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首映週末票房為310萬美元位居第十三名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Screams $26M+ Opening, Gives Sony 3rd Summer Cash Cow After ‘Sausage Party’, ‘Shallows’: Early Sunday Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|accessdate=August 28, 2016|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210230212/https://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

